WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.457 --> 00:00:01.349
Good morning, family.

00:00:01.349 --> 00:00:02.240
Praise the Lord!

00:00:02.240 --> 00:00:03.954
It's Brandon and Diana again.

00:00:04.297 --> 00:00:06.804
We have some things on our heart today, folks.

00:00:06.804 --> 00:00:08.897
We're in the last of the last days here.

00:00:08.897 --> 00:00:16.097
Jesus is coming, things are getting serious, and people say, 'Brandon, that kind of scares me.

00:00:16.097 --> 00:00:19.160
' You should be scared if you don't know Jesus.

00:00:19.160 --> 00:00:24.333
You should be flat terrified if you don't have Jesus Christ as your Lord and personal savior.

00:00:24.333 --> 00:00:33.370
It should just plum freak you out if you don't have Jesus as your Lord and personal savior because you are in trouble.

00:00:33.370 --> 00:00:41.440
This is the time right now, as we speak, to yield yourself and say, 'Jesus, I need a savior.

00:00:41.440 --> 00:00:50.462
' You have the opportunity today to make Jesus Christ your Lord and personal savior; to say today, 'I choose to follow Jesus.

00:00:50.462 --> 00:00:52.794
' No one is promised tomorrow.

00:00:53.377 --> 00:00:57.520
Have you driven by a massive graveyard and seen all those people?

00:00:57.859 --> 00:01:05.587
I always wonder how many of those people went to hell and how many went to heaven.

00:01:05.587 --> 00:01:13.791
Everybody has a choice, but everybody thinks they have a long time to make a choice, and some of you only have today.

00:01:13.791 --> 00:01:20.284
Some of you will not make it out of your sleep tonight; some of you won't make it out of your week.

00:01:20.284 --> 00:01:23.942
You are not promised tomorrow; you're only promised right now.

00:01:24.337 --> 00:01:30.280
I believe with all my heart that God is going to give us long life, and He said He'd satisfy us and show us His salvation.

00:01:30.280 --> 00:01:31.380
I believe for 120 years.

00:01:31.380 --> 00:01:34.594
You believe for all this stuff, but sometimes things happen.

00:01:35.023 --> 00:01:42.880
I'm just trying to make you think about eternity today.

00:01:42.880 --> 00:01:45.076
Think about eternity.

00:01:45.333 --> 00:02:09.285
If you look at all the stars in space, if you look at all the grains of sand on the beach, and every single one of those little pieces of grain of sand represent a year—you can count all the sand on a beach, you can count all the stars in the galaxies and the universe, and you still will be counting and counting.

00:02:13.280 --> 00:02:16.417
Eternity is forever, and so that's what I'm trying to tell you all.

00:02:16.417 --> 00:02:20.743
If you really look at how big eternity is, your mind can't comprehend it.

00:02:20.743 --> 00:02:25.636
You can never count all the sand on a beach or the stars in the sky.

00:02:26.053 --> 00:02:45.475
Even if you did, eternity is far greater than that.

00:02:45.475 --> 00:02:58.080
So I want you to focus on your eternity.

00:03:04.640 --> 00:03:07.159
Where will you spend eternity?

00:03:07.599 --> 00:03:19.771
You don't turn into some kind of nothingness.

00:03:19.771 --> 00:03:37.380
We don't have reincarnation and come back as a butterfly or a dog or a cat.

00:03:47.498 --> 00:03:57.484
No, the Bible says it's appointed unto man once to die, and after that the judgment.

00:04:00.436 --> 00:04:27.806
To be absent from the body is to be present with the Lord or to be present in hell, folks.

00:04:27.806 --> 00:04:38.036
Where will you go and spend eternity?

00:04:38.036 --> 00:04:53.400
That's what you have to ask yourself as you watch this today.

00:04:53.400 --> 00:05:16.689
Yes, all this stuff is going on, and I'm telling you tragic things I've seen—very sobering, dark days ahead.

00:05:16.689 --> 00:05:30.506
Most people say, 'Well, that's not for me.

00:05:30.506 --> 00:06:09.591
' A lot of people in the Christian community do not want to hear it because they think we're going to pray it all away.

00:06:09.591 --> 00:06:43.189
Folks, things happen, and I want to tell you COVID wasn't prayed away like you all thought it would be.

00:06:44.331 --> 00:07:03.063
I saw a storm coming and the Lord told me this was a storm to wake up everybody.

00:07:03.063 --> 00:07:09.955
Did He create the storm?

00:07:09.955 --> 00:07:16.120
Did He create COVID?

00:07:16.120 --> 00:07:17.560
No.

00:07:17.560 --> 00:07:50.039
But the Lord told me, 'I've yelled and yelled to tell my bride to wake up, to tell my body to wake up.

00:07:50.039 --> 00:08:18.559
' He said, 'Brandon, what happens to a child if you keep telling them to get up?

00:08:18.559 --> 00:08:20.115
What's the next thing you do?

00:08:20.115 --> 00:08:27.760
' He said, 'You shake them.

00:08:27.760 --> 00:08:43.160
' A great shaking to awaken is about to take place.

00:08:50.475 --> 00:09:08.570
And He told me this: 'If the church does not wake up after this shaking, there will be another shaking.

00:09:08.570 --> 00:09:26.828
A greater wave, a greater shaking is coming for the church.

00:09:26.828 --> 00:10:13.422
' We saw a lot of people wake up during this timeframe, but there are still billions that are asleep, that do not see how close we are to the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:10:13.422 --> 00:10:29.485
They rouse themselves and then just fall back asleep.

00:10:29.485 --> 00:10:48.385
They look up and go, 'Oh, okay,' and they go back to sleep.

00:10:48.385 --> 00:10:51.430
That's what happened.

00:10:51.430 --> 00:11:15.529
So now I really believe, whenever Jonathan Cahn talked about the lightning strikes, I thought that was amazing.

00:11:16.893 --> 00:11:32.750
I encourage you to go watch that video, Jonathan Cahn's lightning strike.

00:11:34.370 --> 00:12:18.504
He talked about how lightning struck the One World Trade Center, the Empire State Building, the Capitol, and the Washington Monument, and he said this was not coincidence.

00:12:27.440 --> 00:12:33.942
It all happened before the new year of 2025.

00:12:33.942 --> 00:12:40.275
It's a sign.

00:12:40.275 --> 00:12:53.320
I thought it was interesting it was four again.

00:12:55.491 --> 00:13:19.895
The Lord told me, 'I'm giving you a four-year window for a massive harvest.

00:13:19.895 --> 00:13:47.260
I'm giving you a reprieve from what was coming, a major reprieve from a great acceleration of the Antichrist agenda upon this earth.

00:13:47.260 --> 00:14:19.140
' I told you we were at the end of the last Shemitah cycle timeframe of this last Rosh Hashanah.

00:14:20.010 --> 00:14:30.884
And He told me, 'Adam's lease is up.

00:14:30.884 --> 00:14:50.955
' But He's giving us a sliver of time to bring in the harvest.

00:14:50.955 --> 00:15:04.239
Satan is petitioning for the seven-year Tribulation, saying time is up.

00:15:04.239 --> 00:15:18.660
That's where we are, folks, and God's giving us this little window.

00:15:18.660 --> 00:16:01.199
I believe through Trump's presidency of these four years, the four lightning strikes, the four oak trees I've told you about—the Lord said, 'Brandon, I'm kicking this down the road.

00:16:01.199 --> 00:16:08.479
I'm giving you a window.

00:16:23.320 --> 00:16:23.626
I want a harvest.

00:16:23.626 --> 00:16:44.860
' Jesus held out His hands with those massive holes and said, 'I am the Lord of the harvest.

00:16:44.860 --> 00:16:51.782
Will you help me?

00:16:51.782 --> 00:17:03.031
For I died for every single one of them.

00:17:03.031 --> 00:17:27.400
' He wants every single one of you to have the opportunity to choose heaven today.

00:17:27.400 --> 00:18:05.974
You're here because you want to know about terrorist attacks; I'm telling you something much worse is coming than you could ever imagine: it's called hell.

00:18:05.974 --> 00:18:14.060
You have the opportunity today to choose heaven.

00:18:15.820 --> 00:18:33.977
God didn't create hell for human beings; He created it for the devil and his demons.

00:18:33.977 --> 00:18:48.853
He created heaven for you, but it's a choice.

00:18:48.853 --> 00:18:55.144
Whom will you serve this day?

00:18:56.512 --> 00:19:12.559
As for me and my house, we're serving the Lord.

00:19:12.559 --> 00:19:26.293
Jesus Christ is the only way to heaven.

00:19:26.293 --> 00:19:40.370
Not Buddha, not Muhammad, not any kind of false god.

00:19:42.644 --> 00:20:02.400
I got an email from a guy saying there's a lot of ways to heaven.

00:20:02.400 --> 00:20:15.280
No, sir, you are deceived by a demonic spirit.

00:20:15.280 --> 00:20:25.578
The only way is the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:20:25.578 --> 00:20:39.366
We believe on this channel that He's coming soon.

00:20:46.344 --> 00:21:09.662
I had a guy email saying he wants to party in his 20s and give his heart to Jesus in ten years.

00:21:09.662 --> 00:21:15.640
Is that a serious question?

00:21:15.640 --> 00:21:29.293
God's not good enough for you right now?

00:21:29.293 --> 00:22:15.290
That's the attitude of a lot of people, and I say, 'Woe to you,' because there will be a day you stand before the Father and give an account for everything you've done.

00:22:15.290 --> 00:22:22.880
He will either know you or say, 'Depart from me, I never knew you.

00:22:22.880 --> 00:22:33.154
' It's a bad eternity for you.

00:22:33.154 --> 00:22:44.480
I've seen a great economic crisis beyond comprehension.

00:22:44.480 --> 00:22:57.950
The Lord said it was delayed for a window.

00:22:57.950 --> 00:23:32.639
There's a word for my body, for the people who are on fire and filled with the Holy Spirit, to have their lamps full of oil.

00:23:37.409 --> 00:24:01.579
And for the ones living lukewarm, there's a separate word: there will be a great shaking to awaken again for them.

00:24:01.579 --> 00:24:21.974
He's a God of mercy, giving one last chance to get on the boat.

00:24:23.456 --> 00:24:32.640
The ark is about to be sealed shut.

00:24:32.640 --> 00:24:40.035
You're running out of time.

00:24:40.035 --> 00:24:50.500
Checking your heart: who is your Lord?

00:25:02.807 --> 00:25:03.253
We have a window here.

00:25:04.146 --> 00:25:15.360
In 2025, a great shaking is coming.

00:25:15.360 --> 00:25:44.382
I've heard some people say it would be a year of war, and that's exactly what I heard: war, war, war.

00:25:45.205 --> 00:25:51.399
And we will see great financial provision.

00:25:51.399 --> 00:26:23.645
What makes you stand out and show that God is a good God if you're broke, busted, and disgusted, sick, and always depressed?

00:26:31.900 --> 00:26:33.240
The world is attracted to life.

00:26:33.240 --> 00:27:05.569
That's why they fake it so much in Hollywood with Botox and fillers and face lifts; they're trying to cover up who they truly are.

00:27:14.824 --> 00:27:29.439
But when you have a light on your face and a song in your heart, people see it.

00:27:29.439 --> 00:27:37.434
They feel the presence of the Holy Spirit on you.

00:27:37.434 --> 00:27:58.220
Material things are never going to fill that empty void in your heart.

00:28:00.285 --> 00:28:13.733
You yield yourself to the Prince of Peace.

00:28:13.733 --> 00:28:38.559
He's the one who's going to renew your mind from all the hell you've let in.

00:28:38.559 --> 00:28:49.891
Garbage in, garbage out; peace in, peace out.

00:28:49.891 --> 00:28:59.919
Think on things that are pure and holy.

00:28:59.919 --> 00:29:23.000
People continue to do the same thing expecting different results; that is the definition of insanity.

00:29:25.280 --> 00:29:36.720
You think you're going to fill this hole with money and perversion?

00:29:47.690 --> 00:29:48.000
You're still going to be empty tomorrow.

00:29:52.733 --> 00:29:58.000
You get wasted at bars and then vomit your guts out.

00:30:07.065 --> 00:30:11.520
The only one that's ever going to satisfy is the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:30:14.915 --> 00:30:15.693
I am addicted to Jesus.

00:30:15.693 --> 00:30:20.376
I am sold out.

00:30:20.376 --> 00:30:29.668
He's changed me from the inside out.

00:30:29.668 --> 00:30:38.215
I have found the source!

00:30:38.215 --> 00:30:45.640
He is life, joy, and peace.

00:30:45.640 --> 00:31:03.559
As you seek His face, He said, 'Give, and it shall be given unto you.

00:31:03.559 --> 00:31:21.564
' The wealth of the sinner is laid up for the righteous.

00:31:21.564 --> 00:31:27.080
Seek first the kingdom.

00:31:27.080 --> 00:32:00.021
He said, 'Brandon, I'll let you have as much overflow as long as it doesn't have you.

00:32:00.021 --> 00:32:18.394
' I will make you a distribution center if you just yield to me.

00:32:18.394 --> 00:32:27.680
All I need is peace and joy.

00:32:27.680 --> 00:32:48.973
A vessel leaks, and you've got to keep being filled with the Holy Spirit.

00:32:48.973 --> 00:32:57.110
You've got to fill it up with the water of the Word, having fellowship with Him.

00:32:57.110 --> 00:33:17.149
I know there's a lot of you desperate for change in 2025.

00:33:17.149 --> 00:33:27.013
You have to raise your praise level.

00:33:27.013 --> 00:33:35.127
When praises go up, blessings come down.

00:33:35.127 --> 00:33:42.571
Keep it vertical with the Lord.

00:33:42.571 --> 00:34:19.440
If you're not in sync with Him on what to do with your money, you'll lose it in a 24-hour period.

00:34:19.440 --> 00:34:32.800
Are you all in for Jesus today?

00:34:32.800 --> 00:34:43.480
Perfect love casts out all fear.

00:34:43.480 --> 00:34:49.170
God is our protector.

00:34:55.973 --> 00:35:14.217
We were listening to Pastor Chip tonight about Maria Woodworth-Etter in the 1930s during the Great Depression.

00:35:27.359 --> 00:35:42.440
They had no food, but they set their plates and prayed by faith, and somebody would knock on their door supernaturally.

00:35:45.079 --> 00:35:55.511
We will live in the supernatural in the days ahead.

00:36:04.619 --> 00:36:12.429
I saw a window of opportunity to get your house in order.

00:36:12.429 --> 00:36:42.919
People are going to flee from the East Coast and West Coast to the central part of America for a major revival.

00:36:42.919 --> 00:37:00.160
I saw Woodstock taking place all over the nation.

00:37:00.160 --> 00:37:12.455
It's a time to get your heart right.

00:37:15.880 --> 00:37:24.253
I want to give everyone an opportunity to accept Jesus.

00:37:24.253 --> 00:37:34.810
We're going to say the sinner's prayer.

00:37:34.810 --> 00:38:06.867
Romans 10:9-10 says if you confess with your mouth and believe in your heart, you will be saved.

00:38:06.867 --> 00:38:30.200
Say, 'Jesus, I want to make you my Lord and personal savior.

00:38:43.430 --> 00:38:45.319
I believe You died and rose again.

00:38:45.319 --> 00:38:51.326
Forgive me of my sins.

00:38:51.326 --> 00:39:06.417
Today I'm turning my back on the world and looking to You.

00:39:07.660 --> 00:39:15.440
Thank You for washing my sins away.

00:39:15.440 --> 00:39:24.700
' If you said that, you're born again.

00:39:24.700 --> 00:39:37.871
Find a Bible-believing church, get water baptized, and tell people.

00:39:37.871 --> 00:39:55.160
It will help you get strong to stand against the devil.

00:39:55.160 --> 00:40:05.153
It's time to put on your armor.

00:40:05.153 --> 00:40:10.462
Feed your faith on the Word.

00:40:15.331 --> 00:40:30.160
Now we're going to pray for President Trump, the inauguration, and the fires in California.

00:40:30.160 --> 00:40:34.023
We take communion.

00:40:34.023 --> 00:40:44.395
Lord, we thank You that by Your stripes we are healed.

00:40:44.395 --> 00:40:59.053
We plead the blood of Jesus over our finances, jobs, and homes.

00:40:59.053 --> 00:41:14.830
We lift up President Trump and bind the demonic attack concerning this trial.

00:41:14.830 --> 00:41:23.231
We say, 'Satan, get your hands off.

00:41:23.231 --> 00:41:33.400
' No weapon formed against him shall prosper.

00:41:35.309 --> 00:41:42.540
We pray the angels protect him and his family.

00:41:47.124 --> 00:41:51.909
We call for a holy conviction over these prosecutors.

00:41:52.177 --> 00:42:08.535
We pray over the fires in California and say, 'Fires, stop now.

00:42:08.535 --> 00:42:19.040
' We call the angels to put them out.

00:42:20.269 --> 00:42:34.074
We pray for protection against any kind of attacks on this nation.

00:42:34.074 --> 00:42:42.039
Let everything hidden be revealed.

00:42:42.039 --> 00:42:59.640
We call for revival over this beautiful nation, Asia, the Middle East, and Russia.

00:43:09.511 --> 00:43:14.994
We thank You for the financial outpouring to support the gospel.

00:43:14.994 --> 00:43:21.599
Diana, pray over the babies.

00:43:23.880 --> 00:43:28.822
Father, we speak to these women's wombs.

00:43:28.822 --> 00:43:38.760
We thank You that everything is functioning as it should.

00:43:38.760 --> 00:43:48.319
We call for healthy pregnancies and easy deliveries.

00:43:59.846 --> 00:44:03.891
These babies will come forth healed and whole, with no neurological difficulties.

00:44:12.988 --> 00:44:13.291
We pray they have perfect Apgar scores.

00:44:13.291 --> 00:44:22.848
We pray for godly homes and strong marriages.

00:44:29.839 --> 00:44:30.079
We pray against SAD, Seasonal Affective Disorder.

00:44:30.079 --> 00:44:35.895
We have the mind of Christ.

00:44:35.895 --> 00:44:42.967
We rebuke autoimmune and thyroid disorders.

00:44:42.967 --> 00:44:54.470
Today, something good is happening for me!

00:44:57.189 --> 00:45:05.720
We thank You for the blood of Jesus.

00:45:05.720 --> 00:45:12.200
Lord, we give You praise.

00:45:12.200 --> 00:45:14.571
Amen.

00:45:14.571 --> 00:45:26.040
If you're new here, please subscribe.

00:45:26.040 --> 00:45:34.189
It helps the algorithm spread the gospel.

00:45:43.040 --> 00:45:47.245
It's all about getting Jesus spread throughout the whole world.

