Our new Spanish channel, Last Days Español, is going.

00:46:03.650 --> 00:46:09.059
We have channels in Chinese, Korean, Vietnamese, and Russian.

00:46:09.059 --> 00:46:23.680
We're spreading the word because we're running out of time.

00:46:23.680 --> 00:46:32.305
Thank you for supporting us.

00:46:32.305 --> 00:46:51.400
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:46:51.400 --> 00:46:56.650
Jesus loves you.

00:46:56.650 --> 00:46:58.271
God bless you.
